<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>예약 완료 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
  {{> components/header}}
  
  <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      {{^reservation}}
      <div class="text-center py-20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">예약 정보가 없습니다.</h2>
        <a href="/reservations" class="mt-4 px-6 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg inline-block">처음으로 돌아가기</a>
      </div>
      {{/reservation}}

      {{#reservation}}
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-10 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600"></i>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">예약이 완료되었습니다!</h1>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mb-10"><span class="font-semibold">{{name}}</span>님의 진료 예약이 성공적으로 접수되었습니다.</p>

          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-left space-y-6 border border-slate-100 mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b border-slate-200 pb-4 mb-4">예약 상세 정보</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-6 gap-x-12">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i data-feather="user" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">환자명</div>
                  <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{name}}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i data-feather="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1">진료과 / 전문의</div>
                  <div class="font-medium text-slate-800">{{dept}} / {{doctor}}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm inline-block">메인으로 가기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/reservation}}
    </div>
  </main>

  {{> components/footer}}
  <script>feather.replace();</script>
</body>
</html>